        <a href="#fnref-1" class="footnote-back" aria-label="Voltar ao texto da nota 1">↩</a>
      </li>
      <li id="fn-2">
        Guyatt GH. Evidence-based medicine. <em>ACP J Club</em> 1991;114(2):A16.
        <a href="#fnref-2" class="footnote-back" aria-label="Voltar ao texto da nota 2">↩</a>
      </li>
      <li id="fn-3">
        Sackett DL, Rosenberg WMC, Gray JAM, Haynes RB, Richardson WS. Evidence based medicine: what it is and what it isn't. <em>BMJ</em> 1996;312(7023):71–2. Disponível em: <a href="https://www.bmj.com/content/312/7023/71" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">bmj.com/content/312/7023/71</a>.
        <a href="#fnref-3" class="footnote-back" aria-label="Voltar ao texto da nota 3">↩</a>
      </li>
